metadata.name: Lost In a Lost Word
metadata.description: Bridges connects different sides. We will all "pass" somewhen. Photos taken at Galata Bridge Istanbul/Turkey. Galata Bridge is one of the bridges on Golden Horn /Istanbul. Attracts many visitors. When light conditions are suitable geometry of the construction provides nice shadows. This shot was finalist at Miami Street Photo Festival 2019 and Moment Street Photograpy Awards 2019.
